strong><em>《古墓丽影》</em>明星雪莱金发女郎亮相</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="雪莉·金发，劳拉·克劳馥的配音。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Shelley-Blond-Tomb-Raider-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617057" class="wp-caption-text">雪莉·金发，劳拉·克劳馥的配音。图片来源：凯特·格林/英国电影和电视艺术学院/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>雪莉·金发 (Shelley Blonde <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gamers-vote-lara-croft-as-the-most-iconic-character-in-gaming-3612798">) 饰演的角色劳拉·克劳馥 (Lara Croft) 被评为游戏界最具标志性的角色</a>几天后，人们发现她在英国电影和电视艺术学院游戏 (BAFTA Games) 的后台庆祝。</p><h3><strong>蜘蛛侠归来</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617054" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617054" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617054" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood.jpg" alt="纳吉·杰特和大卫·哈伍德。图片来源：BAFTA，盖蒂图片社" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Nadji-Jeter-and-David-Harewood-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617054" class="wp-caption-text">纳吉·杰特和大卫·哈伍德。图片来源：Scott Garfitt / BAFTA via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>纳吉·杰特 (Nadji Jeter) 回归，但这次他带着奖项，大卫·哈伍德 (David Harewood) 因其在迈尔斯·莫拉莱斯 (Miles Morales) 中的表演而授予他“最佳表演者”奖。</p><h3> <strong>“取景器”团队度过了一个盛大的夜晚</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617058" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617058" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617058" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="乔治·巴克、格温德林·福斯特和马修·斯塔克庆祝“取景器”。图片来源：BAFTA 的 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Viewfinder-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617058" class="wp-caption-text">乔治·巴克、格温德林·福斯特和马修·斯塔克庆祝“取景器”。图片来源：Shane Anthony Sinclair / BAFTA / Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>很少有团队能像 Sad Owl Studios 那样值得庆祝，这家苏格兰开发商是华丽的独立热门游戏《Viewfinder》的开发商——请务必观看他们<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cy8yJqxpbo0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">激动人心的最佳英国游戏获奖感言</a>。</p><h3><strong>后台与今晚的表演者一起</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617053" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617053" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617053" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA.jpg" alt="朱莉·埃尔文、丹尼尔·奥茨和亚伦·格莱姆斯。图片来源：BAFTA 的 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Julie-Elven-Daniel-Oates-Aaron-Grimes-BAFTA-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617053" class="wp-caption-text">朱莉·埃尔文、丹尼尔·奥茨和亚伦·格莱姆斯。图片来源：凯特·格林/英国电影和电视艺术学院/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>Julie Elven（左）、Daniel Oates（中）和 Aaron Grimes（右）翻唱了 Poets Of The Fall 的歌曲《Late Goodbye》，向游戏行业失去的人们致敬。</p><h3> <strong>《博德之门 3》统治了夜晚</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617050" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617050" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617050" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg" alt="Larian Studios 在 BAFTA Games 评选最佳游戏" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/BAFTA-Games-Baldurs-Gate-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.